 (405140009), <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1692317&amp;fLockTerm=Smoking+cessation+assistance">Smoking cessation assistance</a>
 (384742004), <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C4075828&amp;fLockTerm=Smoking+cessation+drug+therapy">Smoking cessation drug therapy</a>
 (713700008), <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1621885&amp;fLockTerm=Smoking+cessation+education">Smoking cessation education</a>
 (225323000), <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C1095963&amp;fLockTerm=Smoking+cessation+therapy">Smoking cessation therapy</a>
 (710081004), <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0040332&amp;fLockTerm=Tobacco+dependence+syndrome">Tobacco dependence syndrome</a>
 (89765005)                    </div>
                    <!-- /.field-content -->
                </div>
                <!-- /.field -->
    </div>
        <!-- /.content-tab-panel -->
            <div id="neats-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
                <p id="NeatsDescription">
                    National Guideline Clearinghouse (NGC) has assessed this guideline's adherence to standards of trustworthiness, derived from the Institute of Medicine's report
                    <a href="/web/20180712205914/https://www.guideline.gov/disclaimer?id=51056&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3A%2F%2Fnationalacademies.org%2Fhmd%2FReports%2F2011%2FClinical-Practice-Guidelines-We-Can-Trust.aspx"><i>Clinical Practice Guidelines We Can Trust</i></a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712205914im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif">.
